* Geometry
* Linear Transformation
* Affine Space
* Affine Transformation
* Orientation
  * Euler Angles
  * Quaternions
* Projection
  * Perspective
  * Orthogonal
* Curves
  * Spline
    * Bezier
    * Catmull–Rom
    * Hermite

