## Game Physics #2

### Collision Detection
* Bounding Volume
  * AABB
  * OBB
* Broad Phase
  * Spatial Partitioning
    * BVH
    * DBVT
    * Sort and Sweep
* Narrow Phase
  * Intersection
    * SAT
    * GJK
    * EPA
* Convexity
  * Convex
    * Convex Hull
  * Concave
    * Convex Decomposition
* CCD (Continuous Collision Detection)

